CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 9, 1954, page 17, reads: "Leaders Meet - Robert E. (Pappy) Williams, Fifth Ward Chairman, extends his best wishes to his political associate of more than twenty years."
TitMainTitle: Robert E. "Pappy" Williams shaking hands with Paul F. Jones, standing in office interior with floral arrangement on filing cabinets in the City County Building
